<div class="row">
  <div class="col -xs-12">
    <div class="rw-planet-pulse">
      <header class="planet-pulse-header">
        {{#unless pulseSelected}}
          <h1 class="planet-pulse-title">Planet pulse</h1>
        {{/unless}}
        <ul class="planet-pulse-nav">
          {{#each categories}}
            <li class="planet-pulse-nav-link">
            {{#if this.isActive}}
              <a class="is-active" href="#{{this.category}}" id="{{this.category}}">{{this.category}}</a>
            {{else}}
              <a class="" href="#{{this.category}}" id="{{this.category}}">{{this.category}}</a>
            {{/if}}
            </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
        <div class="planet-pulse-toolbar">
          <a href="#">Back</a>
          <button id="fullscreenBtn">Fullscreen</button>
        </div>
      </header>
      <div class="planet-pulse-content">
        {{#each category}}
        {{/each}}
        <article id="paco">
          <h2>Title</h2>
          <p>Lorem fistrum amatomaa commodo laboris papaar papaar condemor a peich benemeritaar. Quis adipisicing condemor tiene musho peligro labore nisi consectetur. Cillum ut pupita qui diodeno eiusmod magna ut. Dolor incididunt apetecan ut. Benemeritaar a wan no te digo trigo por no llamarte Rodrigor esse exercitation mamaar aliquip incididunt no puedor sit amet. Qui est√° la cosa muy malar qui amatomaa exercitation commodo. Laboris sexuarl por la gloria de mi madre aliquip eiusmod.</p>
          <h3>Layers</h3>
          <ul>
            {{#each layers}}
            {{/each}}
            <li><a class="is-disabled is-link">Droughts (SPEI)</a></li>
            <li><a class="planet-pulse-layer" href="#drought/agriculture">Agricultural areas (EarthStat)</a></li>
            <li><a class="planet-pulse-layer" href="#drought/grace">GRACE Groundwater trend<span data-modal="grace" class="btn-info modal-link"><svg><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="#icon-info"></use></svg></span></a></li>
